# Private business documents — never ship to the public site repo.
# contracts/      : signed agreements (BAAs, MSAs, etc.) — PII + legal terms
# private/        : working business notes (pricing, customer prep, internal drafts)
# proposals/      : customer-facing drafts in progress
# agent-reports/  : agent output (drift reports, summaries) — references private outreach
# corpus/         : Lantern Harbor prospect corpus (~5,113 business records,
#                   outreach drafts, fingerprint data). Names, addresses,
#                   principal contacts, in-progress outreach for South Shore
#                   businesses. Lives on disk; may move to a separate private
#                   repo later.
contracts/
private/
proposals/
agent-reports/
corpus/
